<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
  
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Background Image -->
  <div class="background-image"></div>
  
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
  
  <main class="main-content">
    <%- include('partials/messages') %>
    
    <section class="about-section">
      <div class="about-header">
        <h1 class="about-title">Contact Us</h1>
        <p class="about-subtitle">Get in touch with the VigilCam team</p>
      </div>

      <div class="social-grid" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <a href="mailto:azhaanalisiddiqui15@gmail.com" class="social-card email">
          <div class="social-icon">
            <span class="material-icons" style="font-size: 3.5rem; color: #ea4335;">email</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="social-name">Email Us</h3>
          <p class="social-handle">azhaanalisiddiqui15@gmail.com</p>
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/azhaanalisiddiqui/" target="_blank" class="social-card linkedin">
          <div class="social-icon">
            <span class="material-icons" style="font-size: 3.5rem; color: #0077b5;">work</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="social-name">LinkedIn</h3>
          <p class="social-handle">Connect Professionally</p>
        </a>

        <a href="https://github.com/AzhaanGlitch" target="_blank" class="social-card github">
          <div class="social-icon">
            <span class="material-icons" style="font-size: 3.5rem;">code</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="social-name">GitHub</h3>
          <p class="social-handle">View Projects</p>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact Information -->
      <div style="margin-top: 4rem; text-align: center; padding: 2rem; background: var(--bg-card); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 0.8rem;">
          <span class="material-icons">support_agent</span>
          Support Information
        </h3>
        <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          For technical support, bug reports, or feature requests, please reach out via:
        </p>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; text-align: left; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; padding: 1rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border-radius: 8px;">
            <span class="material-icons" style="color: #00ffff;">email</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Email:</strong> azhaanalisiddiqui15@gmail.com<br>
              <small style="color: var(--text-muted);">Response within 24-48 hours</small>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; padding: 1rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border-radius: 8px;">
            <span class="material-icons" style="color: #00ffff;">bug_report</span>
            <div>
              <strong>GitHub Issues:</strong> Report bugs and request features<br>
              <small style="color: var(--text-muted);">Public issue tracker</small>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; padding: 1rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border-radius: 8px;">
            <span class="material-icons" style="color: #00ffff;">description</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Documentation:</strong> Check our comprehensive guides<br>
              <small style="color: var(--text-muted);">README.md</small>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Section -->
      <div style="margin-top: 4rem;">
        <h3 style="font-size: 2rem; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          <span class="material-icons" style="vertical-align: middle; font-size: 2.5rem;">help</span>
          Frequently Asked Questions
        </h3>
        <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem;">
          <details style="background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.5rem;">
            <summary style="cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">
              <span class="material-icons" style="font-size: 1.2rem;">videocam</span>
              How accurate is the face detection?
            </summary>
            <p style="margin-top: 1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6;">
              VigilCam uses MediaPipe Face Mesh with 468 facial landmarks, providing industry-leading accuracy. 
              The system detects faces with 95%+ confidence and tracks micro-movements including eye gaze, 
              blinks, and mouth movement with sub-pixel precision.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details style="background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.5rem;">
            <summary style="cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">
              <span class="material-icons" style="font-size: 1.2rem;">settings</span>
              Can I adjust detection sensitivity?
            </summary>
            <p style="margin-top: 1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6;">
              Yes! Edit the configuration constants in <code>vigilcam_stream.py</code> to adjust thresholds 
              for gaze tracking, blink detection, audio sensitivity, and more. See the SETUP_GUIDE.md for details.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details style="background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.5rem;">
            <summary style="cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">
              <span class="material-icons" style="font-size: 1.2rem;">privacy_tip</span>
              Is the data secure?
            </summary>
            <p style="margin-top: 1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6;">
              All video processing happens locally on your machine - no video data is stored or transmitted. 
              Only detection statistics and violation logs are saved. User authentication uses bcrypt hashing 
              and secure session management.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details style="background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.5rem;">
            <summary style="cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">
              <span class="material-icons" style="font-size: 1.2rem;">devices</span>
              What are the system requirements?
            </summary>
            <p style="margin-top: 1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6;">
              <strong>Minimum:</strong> Any computer with a webcam, Python 3.8+, Node.js 18+, 4GB RAM<br>
              <strong>Recommended:</strong> Modern CPU (i5/Ryzen 5 or better), 8GB RAM, dedicated GPU (optional but improves performance)<br>
              <strong>Browser:</strong> Chrome, Firefox, Edge, or Safari with camera/microphone permissions
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  
  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>